ata. We choose the\nPOI recommendation as our test scenario; however, the insights should be\ntrivially extendable on other domains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 27 Feb 2022 08:02:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Apr 2022 09:48:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-11"}
